cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use the pccx KV260 RTL or driver source, please cite it using
  the metadata in this file.  When citing the wider project, please
  also reference the canonical architecture repository (`pccx`) listed
  under `references:` below.
title: "pccx-FPGA-NPU-LLM-kv260 — Kria KV260 RTL implementation of pccx v002"
abstract: >-
  An early SystemVerilog RTL and bare-metal driver source snapshot for
  the pccx v002 NPU architecture targeting Xilinx Kria KV260.  This
  repository is a reference implementation, not a timing-closed
  production bitstream release.
type: software
license: Apache-2.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/hkimw/pccx-FPGA-NPU-LLM-kv260"
url: "https://hkimw.github.io/pccx/"
authors:
