    title: "pccx — open FPGA-oriented LLM inference accelerator"
    repository-code: "https://github.com/hkimw/pccx"
    notes: "Canonical architecture, ISA, and docs that this repo implements."
keywords:
  - FPGA
  - SystemVerilog
  - Xilinx Kria KV260
  - Zynq UltraScale+
  - LLM inference
  - W4A8 quantization
  - GEMM
